Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会原谅痴汉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏高西小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,痴汉减少了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我们学校的女生能安心上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 高西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说过传说中的痴汉的传闻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有听说过传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  是传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然大家都觉得是虚构的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:02:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,最近和传闻一样\N痴汉出现的很频繁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,被盯上的都是人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,而且他们都很有感觉\N没有提出受害报告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,跟传闻很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不过现实里不可能会有女性\N在电车上有感觉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,应该只是传闻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,听说这次的犯人是我们的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.46,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.10,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然传闻不可信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被抓到的人是我们的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找人进行巡查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可是完全没有头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们询问了女性被害者\N关于痴汉的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好像这个犯人\N是我们的学生没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,所以找我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,高西小姐抓痴汉很有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我觉得这个事情\N由你来处理应该更有把握
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在警察之前找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,把他找出来\N拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人妻引诱调查\N痴汉电车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,被害人的特征是\N穿短裙的人妻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只好扮演人妻了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看来很难出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他会摸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可是怎么只摸一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底在着急什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,下面变热了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不能让他跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,他露出真面目之前\N稍微忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样摸法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要赶快抓他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法反抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.67,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,会有感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.36,0:14:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没事把
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我尽然对痴汉有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:15:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.28,0:16:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在电车上被痴汉摸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么在我们学校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.36,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不能做痴汉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是校长拜托你来抓痴汉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,然而自己却很爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.58,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我的目的不是抓痴汉\N是让痴汉改过自新
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.50,0:17:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,让我听听姐姐的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.98,0:17:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.12,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你有感觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,让我确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有感觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.02,0:18:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有人来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在上课
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.17,0:18:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,没人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.01,0:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,腰动起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这样摸很爽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,来亲亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,解开了哦\N住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 不要开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.65,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了呢\N住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里敏感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不能摸\N告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.12,0:20:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,奶头硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.38,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.42,0:21:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这样摸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.26,0:21:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:21:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让你更爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.57,0:22:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.35,0:22:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也想要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我摸哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不要摸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.30,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.44,0:23:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡的味道\N真的不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.75,0:23:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,一起爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.67,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能这样做\N你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,被摸了很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.18,0:24:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N屁股真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.73,0:24:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.96,0:24:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.69,0:24:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.95,0:24:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.10,0:25:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,想要肉棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.43,0:25:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.07,0:25:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.64,0:25:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.21,0:25:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.46,0:25:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.70,0:25:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽的吧\N不能摸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.47,0:25:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.97,0:25:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.20,0:26:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.64,0:26:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.67,0:26:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.47,0:26:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.85,0:26:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.62,0:26:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.13,0:26:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.30,0:26:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.73,0:26:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.20,0:26:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,摸了变的这么湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.34,0:26:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
